<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head>	<meta charset="GBK">	<title>预览</title>	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,height=device-height,initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" />	<style type="text/css">	body, div, dl, dt, dd, ul, ol, li, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, pre, form, fieldset, input, textarea, p, blockquote, table, tbody, tfoot, thead, th, td { margin: 0; padding: 0; }table { border-spacing: 0; border-collapse: collapse; }fieldset, img { vertical-align: top; border: 0; }ol, ul { list-style: none; }h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 { font-size: 100%; font-weight: normal; }a { cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; color: #595959; }textarea { overflow-y: auto; resize: vertical; outline: 0 none; }.clearfix:before, .clearfix:after { display: table; content: ""; }.clearfix:after { clear: both; }.clear { font-size: 0; clear: both; overflow: hidden; height: 0; }body { font: 12px/1.5 Microsoft YaHei, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; }.useStepWrap .title i, .useStepWrap .item h6, .clickLeft, .clickRight { background-image: url(data:image/jpg;base64,); background-repeat: no-repeat; }.useStepWrap { width: 654px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 33px 0; }    .useStepWrap .title { position: relative; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: solid 1px #b2b2b2; margin: 0 33px 22px; }    .useStepWrap .title h2 { font-size: 36px; line-height: 40px; float: left; padding-left: 50px; color: #3c7dc5; }    .useStepWrap .titleExp.title h2 { padding-left: 62px; }    .useStepWrap .title i { position: absolute; display: block; float: left; width: 40px; height: 40px; }    .useStepWrap .title .scriptUse { top: 2px; background-position: 5px 3px; }    .useStepWrap .title .scriptTrait { height: 50px; background-position: 5px -146px; }    .useStepWrap .title .scriptExp { width: 50px; height: 50px; background-position: 5px -221px; }    .useStepWrap .item h6 { font-size: 30px; line-height: 49px; width: 132px; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; color: #fff; background-position: 0 -67px; margin: 0 33px; }    .useStepWrap .item p, .scriptInfo p { font-size: 30px; line-height: 48px; color: #3c3c3c; margin: 0 33px 15px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; }    .usePicBox { overflow: hidden; position: relative; margin: 0 33px; }    .clickLeft, .clickRight { display: none; width: 40px; height: 40px; position: absolute; top: 130px; z-index: 99; text-indent: -999999px; cursor: pointer; background-position: -5px -306px; }    .clickLeft { left: 5px; }    .clickRight { right: 5px; background-position: -45px -306px; }    .useStepWrap .usePic { position: relative; }    .useStepWrap .usePic li { display: block; padding: 4px 0; }    .useStepWrap .usePic li img { width: 100%; }@media screen and (max-width:719px) {    .useStepWrap { box-sizing: border-box; width: 100%; padding: 4% 0; overflow: hidden; }    .useStepWrap .title { margin: 0 4%; }    .useStepWrap .item h6 { margin: 0 4%; }    .useStepWrap .item p, .scriptInfo p { margin: 0 4% 15px; }    .useStepWrap .title.scriptUseTitle i { -webkit-background-size: 67px 132px; background-size: 67px 188px; }    .useStepWrap .title .scriptUse { top: 4px; left: 2px; background-position: 2px 1px; }    .useStepWrap .title.scriptUseTitle h2 { padding-left: 30px; }    .useStepWrap .title i { width: 20px; height: 20px; }    .useStepWrap .title { margin-bottom: 12px; padding-bottom: 10px; }    .useStepWrap .title h2 { font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; padding-left: 30px; }    .useStepWrap .item p, .scriptInfo p { font-size: 18px; line-height: 28px; }    .useStepWrap .item h6 { font-size: 17px; line-height: 36px; width: 83px; margin-bottom: 10px; background-position: 0 -36px; -webkit-background-size: 83px 216px; background-size: 83px 216px; }    .useStepWrap .title .scriptTrait { width: 25px; height: 25px; background-position: 8px -72px; -webkit-background-size: 67px 182px; background-size: 67px 182px; }    .usePicBox { margin: 0 4%; }    .clickLeft { left: 1%; }    .clickRight { right: 5%; }    .useStepWrap .usePic li { }    .useStepWrap .usePic li:last-child { }    .useStepWrap .usePic { margin-bottom: 15px; }    .useStepWrap .usePic li img { max-width: 100%; }    .useStepWrap .title h2 { padding-left: 33px; }    .useStepWrap .title .scriptExp { width: 25px; height: 25px; background-position: 4px -108px; -webkit-background-size: 67px 132px; background-size: 67px 184px; }    .useStepWrap .titleExp.title h2 { padding-left: 35px; }}</style></head><body>	<div class="useStepWrap"><ol id="usePic"><li class="item"><!--##Template Begin#-->				<p><!--##P Begin#-->【雷电、MuMu模拟器】<br>1.&nbsp;需要设置分辨率：宽720、高1280、dpi320。<br>2.&nbsp;在设置里打开ROOT开关。<br><br>详细步骤在置顶【群公告】查看安装教程，QQ群：1044933114（进群答案：偃武）。<br><!--#P End##--></p>				<div class="usePicBox">					<ul class="usePic clearfix"><!--##Img Begin#--><!--#Img End##--></ul>				</div>			<!--#Template End##--></li><li class="item"><!--##Template Begin#-->				<p><!--##P Begin#-->【云手机】<br>1.&nbsp;系统不能超过安卓10（推荐安卓10）；<br>2.&nbsp;运行内存推荐不低于4G；<!--#P End##--></p>				<div class="usePicBox">					<ul class="usePic clearfix"><!--##Img Begin#--><!--#Img End##--></ul>				</div>			<!--#Template End##--></li><li class="item"><!--##Template Begin#-->				<p><!--##P Begin#-->【常见问题】<br>1.&nbsp;如果频繁提示未知界面返回、个别队伍一直不出去采集等问题，请检查其他软件的悬浮窗是否移到合适的位置。（如图所示）<!--#P End##--></p>				<div class="usePicBox">					<ul class="usePic clearfix"><!--##Img Begin#--><li><!--##imgPath Begin#--><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAfQAAAEkCAIAAABWilTyAAAgAElEQVR4Aey96Zck+1nfef8FhA32
